%% Sequence — Live chat message (optimistic UI + Pusher broadcast)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Author
    participant C as Chat UI (optimistic)
    participant A as Server Action<br/>sendChatMessage
    participant CS as ChatService
    participant DB as ChatMessageRepository
    participant P as Pusher
    actor O as Other clients

    U->>C: Type + send message
    C->>C: append optimistic (status: pending, tempId)
    C->>A: sendChatMessageAction(body, fingerprint, tempId)
    A->>A: Zod validate · rate-limit · ban check
    A->>CS: createMessage(...)
    CS->>DB: persist ChatMessage
    DB-->>CS: saved message
    CS->>P: trigger 'new-message' (channel)
    P-->>O: broadcast message
    P-->>C: broadcast message (reconcile tempId)
    CS-->>A: result
    alt success
        A-->>C: ok -> mark delivered
    else failure
        A-->>C: error -> markFailed(tempId)
    end
